# Detection events — 4 separate databases

| Workspace | DB name |
|-----------|---------|
| Person (`cameras`) | `atomo_forge_person` |
| Fire & Smoke (`cameras2`) | `atomo_forge_fire` |
| Face (`cameras3`) | `atomo_forge_face` |
| Safety (`cameras4`) | `atomo_forge_safety` |

- Do **not** merge into one `atomo_forge` or `meshcentral`.
- API requires `workspace` on search/image; POST uses `detectionWorkspace`.
- Migrations: `scripts/sql/events/001_four_workspace_databases.sql`
- Grants: `npm run grant:events-db`
